  <brief_title>Radiation Therapy or No Further Treatment Following Surgery in Treating Patients With Cancer of the Uterus</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Randomized Study of Adjuvant Pelvic Radiotherapy Versus Observation Alone in Patients With Completely Resected, Stage I or II, High-Grade Uterine Sarcoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
